::KitKat::
She got the message. She needed to finish things with Aracnia.
"DarkMouse, go see what our latest gurest want and report to me 
later. I am very busy right now."

DarkMouse::
She got the message on her link "Yeah sure. I'll go."
She walked to the lab and saw the two bots in there.  She put her 
hand on her hip, and looked at them. "KitKat's a little busy. What 
can I help you guys  with?"
